Actually, 189k is seriously out of whack in my opinion.  Just for grins, I was in the bazaar (7th Hammer) yesterday and did a search and one came up for 100k.  I'm not saying that was a good price either, just putting it up for reference because I've been told that 7th Hammer is usually extremely high for bazaar prices.
<br />

<br />
I camped the mob with a couple different groups and then one that I had at the time it dropped:
<br />

<br />
70 Pally w/ ~ 10.5k hp
<br />
69 Bard
<br />
66 Zerker
<br />
65 Cleric (bot'd by zerker because we couldn't find a cleric that night)
<br />
Myself (66 Enchanter)
<br />

<br />
Yep, we only had the 5 of us at the time of the kill.  We had a druid when we were forming up the group, but she crashed out and couldn't get back in.  The bard was getting ready to head out when the Kyv Bowguard spawned.  I did have a 66 war and 68 shaman coming to join us.
<br />

<br />
Bard pulled everything in sight and with the pally stunning on INC! I was able to tash/slow before the mob even got into camp which greatly helped out the zerker/cleric being able to keep up on the heals.
<br />

<br />
A pally for a tank actually worked the best because I could tash/slow so much faster than with the warrior's I'd grouped with there before.
<br />

<br />
Good luck to you.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
